    "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"df60bf18efe7500adba15a8676604475\">VTS</span>-2012-51</b>\n</p><p>An appropriately qualified <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"68d26fb2ede57a3d70931de5d282cefb\">VTSO</span> carrying out supervisory duties in a <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"df60bf18efe7500adba15a8676604475\">VTS</span> Centre on behalf of a <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"df60bf18efe7500adba15a8676604475\">VTS</span> authority.\t\n</p><p><br>\n(VTS33/output/8 refers) \n</p>\n<div class=\"LanguageLinks\">\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #FFFFFF\">\n<td style=\"width: 25px; padding-left: 0em; border-right: 1px solid #aaaaaa;border-left: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-top: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-bottom: 1px solid #EEF3E2;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:25px-Geographylogo.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\" title=\"Languages\"><img alt=\"Languages\" src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/8/82/25px-Geographylogo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></td>\n<td style=\"padding: 1px 1em 0; background: #EEF3E2;\">\n<p><b><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">English</a></b>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"df60bf18efe7500adba15a8676604475\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Vessel Traffic Services\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"68d26fb2ede57a3d70931de5d282cefb\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Vessel Traffic Service Officer\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-defi